{"tha-ap121:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap121:0.2":"Mahaparivaravagga ","tha-ap121:0.3":"Paccupatthanasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap121:1.1":"“Atthadassimhi sugate, ","tha-ap121:1.2":"nibbute samanantara; ","tha-ap121:1.3":"Yakkhayonim upapajjim, ","tha-ap121:1.4":"yasam patto caham tada. ","tha-ap121:2.1":"Dulladdham vata me asi, ","tha-ap121:2.2":"duppabhatam durutthitam; ","tha-ap121:2.3":"Yam me bhoge vijjamane, ","tha-ap121:2.4":"parinibbayi cakkhuma. ","tha-ap121:3.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap121:3.2":"sagaro nama savako; ","tha-ap121:3.3":"Mamuddharitukamo so, ","tha-ap121:3.4":"agacchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap121:4.1":"Kim nu socasi ma bhayi, ","tha-ap121:4.2":"cara dhammam sumedhasa; ","tha-ap121:4.3":"Anuppadinna buddhena, ","tha-ap121:4.4":"sabbesam bijasampada. ","tha-ap121:5.1":"Yo ce pujeyya sambuddham, ","tha-ap121:5.2":"titthantam lokanayakam; ","tha-ap121:5.3":"Dhatum sasapamattampi, ","tha-ap121:5.4":"nibbutassapi pujaye. ","tha-ap121:6.1":"Same cittappasadamhi, ","tha-ap121:6.2":"samam punnam mahaggatam; ","tha-ap121:6.3":"Tasma thupam karitvana, ","tha-ap121:6.4":"pujehi jinadhatuyo. ","tha-ap121:7.1":"Sagarassa vaco sutva, ","tha-ap121:7.2":"buddhathupam akasaham; ","tha-ap121:7.3":"Pancavasse paricarim, ","tha-ap121:7.4":"munino thupamuttamam. ","tha-ap121:8.1":"Tena kammena dvipadinda, ","tha-ap121:8.2":"lokajettha narasabha; ","tha-ap121:8.3":"Sampattim anubhotvana, ","tha-ap121:8.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap121:9.1":"Bhuripanna ca cattaro, ","tha-ap121:9.2":"sattakappasate ito; ","tha-ap121:9.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap121:9.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap121:10.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap121:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap121:10.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap121:11.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma paccupatthanasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap121:12.1":"Paccupatthanasannakattherassapadanam navamam. "}